---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>

    <h1>Textile Bag Printing in Armenia (Yerevan)</h1>

    <p>
      Custom printed textile bags for businesses, shops, cafes, and promotional events.
      Eco-friendly and reusable branding solution.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>What we print</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Canvas shopping bags</li>
      <li>Promotional tote bags</li>
      <li>Branded retail bags</li>
      <li>Event and exhibition bags</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Best for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Retail stores</li>
      <li>Cafes and restaurants</li>
      <li>Corporate giveaways</li>
      <li>Marketing campaigns</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Printing methods</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Silk screen printing for bulk orders</li>
      <li>DTF printing for full-color designs</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advantages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Strong brand visibility</li>
      <li>Reusable eco-friendly product</li>
      <li>Low cost for bulk orders</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>Order Printed Bags</h2>
    <p>
      Send your design, quantity, and bag type. We will calculate price and production time.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/quote">Request a Quote</a>

  </main>
</Layout>